                    "value": "<p>The night parade shouts a series of energetic call-and-responses, dealing [[/r 3d10 # sonic damage]]{3d10 sonic damage} and [[/r 4d6 # mental damage]]{4d6 mental damage} to all creatures in a 10-foot burst within 20 feet (<span data-pf2-saving-throw=\"will\" data-pf2-traits=\"damaging-effect,emotion, mental, sonic\" data-pf2-label=\"Seiya! Soiya! DC\" data-pf2-dc=\"41\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">basic Will</span> save). If the troop is reduced to 8 or fewer squares, this area decreases to a 5-foot burst.</p>"
